snippet.title: Bakery Simulator - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
☛ Wishlist Bakery Simulator on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1031120/Bakery_Simulator/

Get up before dawn and see what it's like to be a baker! Learn to bake several dozen types of bread. Use realistic bakery machines. Deliver orders to stores, earn and invest. Use original recipes or experiment and create your own. 

☛ PlayWay's Facebook Profile - https://www.facebook.com/PlayWayGames
